{"id": "art-106", "label": "Art. 106", "title": "Art. 106: Reguli speciale privind ascultarea", "slug": "art-106", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_224031583\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2592\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_224031583\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 106: Reguli\nspeciale privind ascultarea </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1784268889\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2591\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1784268889\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259;, în timpul audierii unei persoane, aceasta\nprezint&#259; semne vizibile de oboseal&#259; excesiv&#259; sau simptomele unei\nboli care îi afecteaz&#259; capacitatea fizic&#259; ori psihic&#259; de a\nparticipa la ascultare, organul judiciar dispune întreruperea ascult&#259;rii\n&#351;i, dac&#259; este cazul, ia m&#259;suri pentru ca persoana s&#259; fie\nconsultat&#259; de un medic.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1249173547\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2590\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1249173547\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Persoana aflat&#259; în deten&#355;ie poate fi\naudiat&#259; la locul de de&#355;inere prin videoconferin&#355;&#259;, în\ncazuri excep&#355;ionale &#351;i dac&#259; organul judiciar apreciaz&#259;\nc&#259; aceasta nu aduce atingere bunei desf&#259;&#351;ur&#259;ri a procesului\nori drepturilor &#351;i intereselor p&#259;r&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1613314240\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2589\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1613314240\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (2), dac&#259; persoana\naudiat&#259; se afl&#259; în vreuna dintre situa&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la\nart. 90, ascultarea nu poate avea loc decât în prezen&#355;a avocatului la\nlocul de de&#355;inere.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Audierea suspectului sau a\ninculpatului</span></b></p>"}